<emphasis box="[238,366,905,924]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="95">Silidius svihlai</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[372,440,906,925]" pageId="2" pageNumber="95" rank="species">sp. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
1 – holotype, dorsal habitus; 2 – male genitalia, ventral view; 3 – pronotum of male; 4 – pronotum of female. Scale bars represent 1 mm; longer scale bar refers to Figs 2–4.
</paragraph>
